{"tid":2195774,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"民權觀察：聯合國專家多次質疑煽動罪不符國際人權標準","createTime":"2020-09-09T11:31:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-09T14:11:23.000Z","uid":241764,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"e1336b3257411fb5ac531cc2a614e0ccba487bfa","tid":2195774,"uid":241764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T11:31:22.000Z","msg":"民權觀察認為，人民力量副主席譚得志被控涉嫌觸犯「煽動罪」，屬以言入罪，要求當局停止政治檢控，摒棄過時法律條文，聯合國專家及人權事務委員會多次質疑今次案件涉及的「煽動罪」不符合國際人權標準。<br />\n<br />\n民權觀察發聲明表示，聯合國特別報告員今年亦曾經去信特區政府，指本港的煽動罪定義太闊，促請政府修改法例，聯合國人權事務委員會過往3次審議《公約》在香港實施情況時，都關注「煽動罪」的適用範圍。<br />\n<br />\n全文: <a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1548729-20200909.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1548729-20200909.htm&d=Yvf7L03l0%2FKFASkGPCPwg6DCEJE6krTJKQ6%2BfiBCJRk%3D&h=19d1bceb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1548729-20200909.htm&h=5ee9204c\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1548729-20200909.htm</a>"},{"pid":"dc507861c3a7db0950f11ac873809aa320e3e67b","tid":2195774,"uid":226851,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"e1336b3257411fb5ac531cc2a614e0ccba487bfa","tid":2195774,"uid":241764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T11:31:22.000Z","msg":"民權觀察認為，人民力量副主席譚得志被控涉嫌觸犯「煽動罪」，屬以言入罪，要求當局停止政治檢控，摒棄過時法律條文，聯合國專家及人權事務委員會多次質疑今次案件涉及的「煽動罪」不符合國際人權標準。<br />\n<br />\n民權觀察發聲明表示，聯合國特別報告員今年亦曾經去信特區政府，指本港的煽動罪定義太闊，促請政府修改法例，聯合國人權事務委員會過往3次審議《公約》在香港實施情況時，都關注「煽動罪」的適用範圍。<br />\n<br />\n全文: <a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1548729-20200909.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1548729-20200909.htm&d=Yvf7L03l0%2FKFASkGPCPwg6DCEJE6krTJKQ6%2BfiBCJRk%3D&h=19d1bceb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1548729-20200909.htm&h=5ee9204c\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1548729-20200909.htm</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T14:11:23.000Z","msg":"民權觀察係乜水，未聽過嘅。<br />\n有咩成員？ 資金來源？國安要唔要查下？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}